Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time for 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' in cases leading to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and the end of case where activity 'Request Payment occurs

Name: Average resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time it takes 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' after 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time it takes the 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' to be followed by 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average waiting time to the 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' after 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' in cases eventually approved
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and next 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' in cases that are re-submitted and approved
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time for 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' in cases leading to a final rejection
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE occurs

Name: Minimum time it takes 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' to be followed by 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total resolution time of cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' leading to case closure without payment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and the end of case where activity 'Request Payment does not occur
